  "Description": {
    "English": "An upgrade to the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Minotaur</span> Heavy Exocraft Hybrid, the Liquidator is a cutting-edge heavy-duty combat unit, designed to operate in the harshest of environments.<br><br>Installation will significantly improve the Minotaur's <span class=\"name name-technology\">engine and mobility</span> systems.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "作为<span class=\"name name-technology\">弥诺陶洛斯</span>重型混合强化艇的升级版本，清算员是一种尖端的重装作战单元，并且被设计成能够在最险恶的环境中执行任务。<br><br>安装这种腿部组建能够显著改善弥诺陶洛斯的<span class=\"name name-technology\">驱动器以及机动</span>系统。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "清算人是一種尖端耐用戰鬥機體，為<span class=\"name name-technology\">彌諾陶洛斯</span>重型混合強化艇的升級，專為在最嚴苛的環境中運作而設計。<br><br>安裝後會顯著提升彌諾陶洛斯的<span class=\"name name-technology\">引擎和機動性</span>系統。"
  },
